reviewText: Barry Manilow gave a great first special. I remember seeing it on TV and fell in love with him then and now.
You cannot say any more about Barry Manilow but that he is the best entertainer in the world.  I have everything he has ever recorded, including old audio tapes,
I'm a dinosaur that's a die hard Barry Manilow fan in everything he does. However, this production was horrible once you see&hear all other concerts&specials he's done before.
I have misplaced this DVD. I am sure it was a great DVD but I don't know where it is at the moment.
